SELECT 
a.nrocomprobante as tabla1_nrocomprobante,
a.fecha as tabla1_fecha,
a.descripcion as tabla1_descripcion,
a.importedebito as tabla1_importedebito,
c.nrocomprobante as tabla2_nrocomprobante,
c.fecha as tabla2_fecha,
c.descripcion as tabla2_descripcion,
c.importecredito as tabla2_importecredito
FROM 
(SELECT * FROM public.proceso03_auxcomp_extractobbva
WHERE descripcion='PAGO DE FACTURAS/SERVICIOS - P.O.S.')a
INNER JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM public.proceso03_auxcomp_extractobbva
WHERE descripcion='TRANSFERENCIA DE FONDOS CC')c
ON a.fecha = c.fecha 
AND a.nrocomprobante = c.nrocomprobante
AND a.importedebito = c.importecredito
